      }}>{`children.forEach(c => {
      this.getChildByChildId.prime(c.id, c);
});

`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`From there, you instantiate the class once in the Apollo's server configuration. The instantiation will occur at every request, hence no data is mixed between users.`}</p>
